readme:
# grunt-targethtml

Produces html-output depending on grunt target

## Getting Started
Install this grunt plugin next to your project's [grunt.js gruntfile][getting_started] with: `npm install grunt-targethtml`

## Release History
* 8/31/12 - v0.1.0 - Initial release.
